text: Ioesse rubra is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Maurice Pic in 1925, originally under the genus Macrocelosterna. It is known from Thailand, Myanmar, China, Laos, and Vietnam.BioLib.cz - Ioesse rubra. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1925
